South African Gold Production Increased by 0.6% in March From Year Earlier

-- B y   A l a s t a i r   R e e d
-- 
2011-05-12T09:30:22Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-12/south-african-gold-production-increased-by-0-6-in-march-from-year-earlier.html
South African gold production rose
0.6 percent in March from a year earlier, Jean-Pierre
Terblanche, a spokesman for Statistics South  Africa , said by
phone from  Pretoria  today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
